snippet.title: Soar - Official Early Access Trailer | Upload VR Showcase
snippet.description: Explore a massive city, fly with friends, and engage in aerial combat in Soar. Check out the trailer for Soar to see what you can expect from this game, available now in Early Access on Quest.
